item.title: Blankets
item.description: Use our moving blankets to protect large items like funiture, bicycles and appliances while you are loading, unloading and transporting these items. Our Moving Blankets are quilted with an extra batting to give them extra cushioning for extra protection of your items.

item.title: Newsprint
item.description: White unprinted newspaper. Recommended for wrapping fragiles, stemware, small pictures, china. A must to use as a cushioning material when packing china boxes or electronic boxes. Packing paper is a cost-efficient and multi-purpose moving supply designed to protect fragile items. You can use it for surface protection of family heirlooms and other fragile items, to prevent shock and vibration, as well as to fill or stuff fine china and glassware for extra density and protection from movement while transferring your boxes.

item.title: Tape 110
item.description: This is a favorite kind of tape that professional movers use most often. This product is the polymer tape designed for a veriety of packing, splicing and tabbing applications. This tape provides a quick and positive seal under a wide range of temp/humidity conditions. This is a recognized standout and most versitile performer in their product line, with a unique tan color that will blend with blend with most any box sealing application.

item.title: Tape Dispenser
item.description: This professional tape dispenser will hold a standard 3” core of tape and comes fully assembled. It’s lightweight, made of metal and high-impact plastic and built to last.
